    <step order="4">Implement the system commands list (hardcoded base: `/help`, `/clear`, `/export`)</step>
    <step order="5">Implement Redis cache check at the start of `ResolveCommandsAsync`: return cached catalog if hit</step>
    <step order="6">Implement Dataverse query for playbooks filtered by `sprk_recordType = context.RecordType` — retrieve `sprk_triggerphrases` and `sprk_name` fields</step>
    <step order="7">Build playbook command entries from the first trigger phrase of each playbook (converted to a slug for the trigger/id)</step>
