    <step order="10">Merge system + playbook + scope commands into a single list; store in Redis with 5-minute TTL and `cmd-catalog:{tenantId}:{recordType}` key</step>
    <step order="11">Wire `DynamicCommandResolver` into `SprkChatAgentFactory` using factory instantiation</step>
    <step order="12">Run `dotnet build` and verify no errors</step>
    <step order="13">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change task R2-019 status to completed (🔲 → ✅)</step>
  </steps>

